# redis 8.8.0 — false positives: Debian-packaging-specific CVEs
# Surfaced during the 2026-06-13 verify of redis:8.8.0.
# CVE-2022-0543 and CVE-2022-3734 are specific to Debian/Ubuntu Redis packaging where
# the Lua library was shipped as a separate shared library. nixpkgs builds Redis statically
# without the vulnerable Debian-specific Lua packaging. No upstream fix exists because
# it is not a Redis upstream vulnerability.
CVE-2022-0543
CVE-2022-3734

